# valgrind suppression file for CUDA programs; attempts
# suppress leaks and uninitialized memory errors stemming from libcuda
# or the Linux kernel to focus attention on errors in user programs.

## CUDA error suppression
{
   <library CUDA: suppress all leaks originating from library calls>
   Memcheck:Leak
   ...
   obj:/*/libcuda.so*
   ...
}

